highlights.text: EsDeeKid has the most spots on Viral Songs Canada. “4 Raws” is the highest at #11.
“Don’t hide” by So Supa is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Canada at #31.
“One Last Breath - Remix” by ATLiens has been on Viral Songs Canada the longest, at 114 days straight.
“Best Part (feat. H.E.R.)” by Daniel Caesar and H.E.R. is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Canada, up 30 spots at #69.
